{"tid":793731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中⋯贏］《人民日報》：即使加徵25%關稅，中國產品仍具性價比優勢","createTime":"2018-08-25T15:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T16:05:00.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"901d320847f9a5d00e8a57b77f22e16ee6e2c413","tid":793731,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T15:40:19.000Z","msg":"中美貿易關係持續緊張，《人民日報》發文指，即使加徵25%關稅，中國產品仍具性價比優勢。<br />\n <br />\n在美國宣布對340億美元自中國進口的產品加徵關稅後，中國機械鑄造企業安徽應流集團，給所有美國採購商發了一封通知函。得到的回覆是所有美國客戶，都同意由他們消化關稅上漲帶來的成本。<br />\n<br />\n文章稱，美國企業經過精確測算後發現，即使加徵25%的關稅，中國產品相對於美國產品，仍具有性價比優勢。<br />\n<br />\n此外，文章亦指出，在經濟全球化背景下，愈來愈多中國製造業企業深度融入全球產業鏈條，與世界各國企業開展貿易往來，進行產業投資，同時引進和學習國際先進經驗和技術，實現產業轉型升級。<br />\n<br />\n中美兩國企業「你中有我，我中有你」，是合作實現共贏，交流帶來機遇。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/china/article/1926924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F1926924&d=JSpwXFdnBwNi9nVq1hEboS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=9e630016\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/china/article/1926924</a>"},{"pid":"6c30f6e1490a60d0bfcbef4e0c9f6bb413775375","tid":793731,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T15:41:23.000Z","msg":"得啦贏哂啦"},{"pid":"4dcdbbff62f299d4943d14d566b614dc36232e89","tid":793731,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c30f6e1490a60d0bfcbef4e0c9f6bb413775375","tid":793731,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T15:41:23.000Z","msg":"得啦贏哂啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T15:43:23.000Z","msg":"我話ok就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edb4b22c8c6f61b417695e6c1a21803d1f1b007","tid":793731,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T15:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/234345_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F234345_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f24d0a80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f191e653da0c4991d9f99274bfb2da877db6b7a9","tid":793731,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:05:00.000Z","msg":"寫咁大版做咩姐，中國有黨宇宙無敵就得啦"}]}